sequenceDiagram
    participant Browser
    participant Store as Pinia Store
    participant API as Elysia API
    participant Disk as File System
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    Browser->>API: POST /api/v1/files/upload (multipart/form-data)
    API->>API: validasi folder ada
    API->>Disk: tulis uploads/<uuid>.<ext>
    API->>DB: INSERT INTO files (name=asli, storage_path=uuid, ...)
    DB-->>API: FileDto
    API-->>Store: FileDto
    Store->>Store: update childrenMap[folderId] lokal
    Store-->>Browser: Toast "Uploaded ..."
